Show HN: A username availability checker to notify you if they become available
text:
This is something I started building a while back and finally launched today after seeing Elon’s tweet about freeing up Twitter handles.

https://twitter.com/elonmusk/status/1601124219009409024

It works for Twitter, Instagram, Reddit, and Snapchat.

It did have Facebook, YouTube, and TikTok but they recently introduced more restrictions for automated checks.
